  "cmd.audit.long": "Launches an opencode session with the auditor agent to perform an audit.\n\nAvailable audit types:\n  security       Vulnerabilities, injections, secret management, dependencies\n  performance    Memory leaks, N+1, rendering, bundle size, lazy loading\n  architecture   Coupling, cohesion, patterns, layers, technical debt\n  accessibility  WCAG, ARIA, contrast, keyboard navigation, screen readers\n  ecodesign      Carbon footprint, resource weight, unnecessary requests, green patterns\n  observability  Logs, traces, metrics, alerting, correlation, SLI/SLO\n  privacy        GDPR, personal data, consent, retention, minimization",
